Package: prelecciones
Title: Access Puerto Rico Electoral Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Open Data Puerto Rico", email = "opendatapr@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Provides functions to access Puerto Rico electoral data including
    election results and event information. Supports multiple geographic
    aggregation levels and optional spatial data via 'sf'.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/opendatapr/puerto-rico-elections-platform
BugReports: https://github.com/opendatapr/puerto-rico-elections-platform/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
